stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Submitted : User Submits Request
    Submitted --> Pending_Approval : Auto-route to Manager
    Pending_Approval --> Approved : Manager Approves
    Pending_Approval --> Rejected : Manager Rejects
    Approved --> Work_In_Progress : Assigned to Team
    Work_In_Progress --> Resolved : Fulfillment Complete
    Resolved --> Closed : User Confirms
    Rejected --> Closed
    Closed --> [*]
    
    Work_In_Progress --> On_Hold : Awaiting Information
    On_Hold --> Work_In_Progress : Information Received
